room_title: Escape room "Polar Express" by Trapped in Tahoe in South Lake Tahoe
room_address: 3320 Sandy Way, Unit 1, South Lake Tahoe, CA 96150
room_description: The Polar Express is running out of control! We are headed straight for the North Pole and we can't get the train to stop! Santa is preparing for Christmas and we have a bunch of presents on board! With Christmas just around the corner, we can't lose all of these toys and set Santa behind! We need your help to stop the train before it crashes! Help us save Christmas!
